title: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet

embed.description: Imgur: The most awesome images on the Internet.

body: Can someone help me to solve this please ? T_T

replies.body:
I've seen this a few times as of late, and most of the time this is caused by your patcher not being able to grab the online assets for the "Beta Client upgrade" message. I'd recommend working through our [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) to ensure all local settings are compatible with League before we further troubleshoot this.

Let me know if this caused any change.
